    public class Sphere
extends GeometricPrimitive
implements SITBase
    The ontological sphere descriptor.

    This class describes extends the basic GeometricPrimitive by considering also a radius for a sphere, in accord with the ontological structure.

    File: it.emarolab.scene_identification_tagging.realObject.Sphere

    date: 05/06/17
